name: Sword of Achievement
description: Congratulations! You unlocked the "Sword of Achievements" by discovering Hic Et Nunc! Illustrated by Pyramid Guy (aka Kris Kanaly). Made in Illustrator and iMovie. Music by UNKOWN, made with samples of the famous Ricoh 2A03 - the sound chip found within the NES. More about the artist at http://pyramidguy.com.
